summary: Comprehensive testing of Tax Assist web application completed. Backend APIs working perfectly (17/17 tests passed). Frontend functionality verified including landing page, user registration, admin login, and client plan viewing. Main issue identified: session management causing quick logouts.

integration_issues.issue: User sessions expire quickly causing redirects to login page during navigation

passed_tests: Landing page loads with hero section and features
Client can view available tax plans
Tax plans display correctly (Basic Salary Filing ₹999, Business Tax Filing ₹2,999)
Authentication tokens being generated and used
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix session management - JWT tokens appear to expire too quickly causing users to be logged out during navigation. Consider increasing token expiry time or implementing token refresh mechanism.
